***************************************************************************
************************ ProtobetterDynamic *******************************
***************************************************************************

"Because code without data is useless..." - Danrae Pray

This library is a fully-featured c++ version of protobetter which expands upon the previous serialization library with the addition of dynamic-typing and type-introspection capabilities in c++.

***************************************************************************
*************************** Build Steps ***********************************
***************************************************************************

1) Install Qt5 w/ QtCreator
2) Load top-level project
3) Build & run in Qt creator like any other command line Qt app

 
***************************************************************************
*************************** Usage Notes ***********************************
***************************************************************************

- To see the usage of the dynamic API, see ProtobetterTest::TestDynamicAPI() in protobetter_test.cpp
- To see how to use this library w/ *.ptype definitions, see ProtobetterTest::TestBittylicousFromPtypeFile() in protobetter_test.cpp
